name: 🌳✨ bright life ✨🌳
description:
Spring is my birthday season.
I have seen from childhood flowers fall, leaves fall, and I see them grow and shine again.
It is the most beautiful and enchanting process, time and mutation, the regeneration of things saying that everything falls, but everything is reborn, and spreads.
Every year I fall, and I'm reborn in spring, the most beautiful season to love your surroundings.
